```

---

# 18. Check Running Processes

```bash
docker top nginx
```

---

# 19. Inspect Container

```bash
docker inspect nginx
```

Shows

- IP Address
- Volumes
- Ports
- Networks
- Mounts
- Configuration

---

# 20. Container Statistics

```bash
docker stats
```

Shows

- CPU
- Memory
- Network
- Disk I/O

