# Important Directories

| Directory | Purpose |
|------------|----------|
| /etc/nginx | Configuration |
| /usr/share/nginx/html | Website files |
| /var/log/nginx | Log files (if enabled) |
| /var/cache/nginx | Cache |
| /tmp | Temporary files |

