# Nginx Architecture

```
Browser
    │
    ▼
Host Port 80
    │
    ▼
Docker Engine
    │
    ▼
Nginx Container
    │
    ▼
/usr/share/nginx/html/index.html
```

---

# Why Use Nginx?

- Serve HTML, CSS, JavaScript
- Reverse Proxy
- HTTPS (SSL/TLS)
- Load Balancer
- Static Files
- API Gateway

---

